 Uning ismida hayot,
.C             D
 Uning ismida umid
.G              Em
 Uning ismida sevgi,
.C            D  G
 Uning ismida najot

[C1]
.  F                     C
   Udir Sening Qutqaruvching
.  F                  G
   Udir Sening Umidvoring
.  F                    C
   Udir Sening Yupatuvching
.  F     C          D
   Uning ismi Iso Masih.</lyrics>
